TIGER LETS IT SLIP

It wasn’t just shots Tiger Woods was dropping as he let a big F-bomb go at the second — swearing loud enough for broadcasters to pick it up after another rotten drive. But Bubba Watson was in trouble for keeping quiet as the big-hitter failed to shout fore after a wayward shot at the same hole.

